(1, 'English Quick Test', '1', 'Quick Test', '<h5><img src="images/icons/english_flag.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="44" height="32" />   ENGLISH QUICK TEST -- 56 Questions</h5>\r\n<p>This test will give you a quick overview of your DNA Gifts. In this tests you could end up with Gifts of equal value, the longer test are designed to eliminate this factor. In this test you will be limited to 12 seconds per question, if you cannot answer a question in time, it will reappear at the end of the test. Do not think about the questions, but rather go with your first natural response to a question.</p>', 1, 16, 7, 1, 'English', 1, 171, 125, 42, '', '2013-05-14 02:23:21', 0),
(2, 'English Short Test', '1', 'Short Test', '<h5><img src="images/icons/english_flag.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="44" height="32" />   ENGLISH SHORT TEST -- 77 Questions</h5>\r\n<p>This test will give you a better understanding your Dynamic Natural Ability. In this test you will be limited to 12 seconds per question, if you cannot answer a question in time, it will reappear at the end of the test. Do not think about the questions, but rather go with your first natural response to a question.</p>', 0, 12, 10, 1, 'English', 2, 322, 208, 42, '', '2013-05-14 02:23:21', 1),
(3, 'English Medium Test', '1', 'Medium Test', '<h5><a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=3"><img src="images/icons/english_flag.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="44" height="32" /></a>   <a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=3">ENGLISH MEDIUM TEST -- 126 Questions</a></h5>\r\n<p>This test will give you a accurate understanding of your Primary Dynamic Natural Ability. Please note that this test will take at least 18-20 minutes.There are no time constraints on this test. Do not think about the questions, but rather go with your first natural response to a question.</p>', 0, 20, 15, 1, 'English', 3, 237, 167, 42, '', '2013-05-14 02:23:21', 1),
(4, 'Indepth Ability Analysis ', '1', 'Indepth Test', '<h5><a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=4"><img src="images/icons/english_flag.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="44" height="32" /></a>   <a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=4">ENGLISH INDEPTH TEST -- 210 Questions</a></h5>\r\n<p>This test can be done if you want to an in-depth analysis of your Dynamic Natural Ability. This test is recommended if you have 2 or 3 Gifts that are equal in value. This test will reveal your dominant Gift. Please note that this test will take at least 25 minutes.There are no time constraints on this test. Do not think about the questions, but rather go with your first natural response to a question.</p>', 0, 0, 25, 1, 'English', 4, 543, 415, 42, '', '2013-05-14 02:23:21', 1),
(5, 'Afrikaanse Toets', '1', 'Afrikaanse Toets', '<h5><a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=5"><img src="images/icons/South-Africa-Flag-256.png" border="0" alt="" width="51" height="35" /></a>    <a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=6">DINAMIESE STERKTE  "AFRIKAANSE TOETS"</a></h5>\r\n<p>Hierdie Afrikaanse toets sal jou ''n akkurate begrip gee van jou dinamiese sterkte.<span style="font-size: 0.83em; line-height: 1.3em;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>. Neem asseblief kennis dat hierdie toets ongeveer 17 minute sal duur. Daar is geen tyd beperkings op die stellings nie. Moet asseblief nie oor die stellings nadink nie, maar beantwoord dit volgens jou eerste natuurlike reaksie op die vraag. Daar is geen regte of verkeerde antwoorde nie. Die akkuraatheid van die uitslag word algeheel deur u eerlikheid en openheid bepaal. Begin met die reis om jouself te leer ken en geniet dit.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h5><span style="color: #ff0000;">NEEM ASB KENNIS DAT DIE DNS VERSLAG WAT U GAAN ONTVANG IN ENGELS GAAN WEES</span></h5>', 0, 15, 20, 1, 'English', 7, 345, 231, 42, '', '2013-06-24 23:58:56', 1),
(6, 'Afrikaanse Toets 2', '1', 'Afrikaanse Toets', '<h5><a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=6"><img src="images/icons/South-Africa-Flag-256.png" border="0" alt="" width="51" height="35" /></a> <a href="free-test-en?view=test&amp;id=6">DINAMIESE STERKTE "AFRIKAANSE TOETS "</a></h5>\r\n<p>Hierdie toets gee vir u ''n goeie oorsig van u dinamiese sterkte". In hierdie weergawe van die analise is dit moontlik dat u kan opeindig met identiese tellings in twee van die Dinamiese Sterktes, hoewel onwaarskynlik, maar wel moontlik. Die langer toets is ontwerp om hierdie faktore te elimineer. In hierdie toets het u 15 sekondes per stelling. As u nie die vraag in tyd kan antwoord nie, sal die stelling weer verskyn aan die einde van die toets. Moet assebleif nie dink oor die stellings nie, maar antwoord volgens u eerste natuurlike reaksie. Om jou outoriteit en dinamika van jou Dinamiese Sterkte te vertsaan is dit baie belangrik om te weet wat jou top sterkte is. Jou outoriteit is gelee in jou 1ste Gawe</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h5><span style="color: #ff0000;">NEEM ASB KENNIS DAT DIE DNS VERSLAG WAT U GAAN ONTVANG IN ENGELS GAAN WEES</span></h5>', 0, 15, 20, 1, 'English', 6, 200, 138, 42, '', '2013-06-25 04:58:56', 1),
(7, 'Afrikaanse Toets 3', '1', 'Afrikaanse Toets', '<h5><img src="images/icons/South-Africa-Flag-256.png" border="0" alt="" width="51" height="35" /> DNA GIFTS "AFRIKAANSE TOETS "</h5>\r\n<p>Hierdie toets gee vir u ''n baie vinnige oorsig van u DNS Gawes "DNA Gifts". In hierdie korter weergawe van die analise is dit baie moontlik dat u kan opeindig met identiese tellings in twee van die DNA Gawes.  Die langer toets is ontwerp om hierdie faktore te elimineer. In hierdie toets het u 12 sekondes per stelling. As u nie die vraag in tyd kan antwoord nie, sal die stelling weer verskyn aan die einde van die toets. Moet assebleif nie dink oor die stellings nie, maar antwoord volgens u eerste natuurlike reaksie.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h5><span style="color: #ff0000;">NEEM ASB KENNIS DAT DIE DNS VERSLAG WAT U GAAN ONTVANG IN ENGELS GAAN WEES</span></h5>', 1, 12, 20, 1, 'English', 5, 51, 40, 42, '', '2013-06-25 04:58:56', 0),
